### Run the code locally

1. Install dependencies
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

2. Run the server locally
```
python -m server
```

### Deploy the code

1. Set up the server
```
gcloud config set project <PROJECT_ID>
gcloud app deploy app.yaml
```

2. Set up the Cloud Endpoints API
```
gcloud endpoints services deploy openapi.yaml
```

3. Set up the Cloud Scheduler
```
gcloud scheduler jobs create http <JOB_NAME> --schedule "0 * * * *" --uri=<ENDPOINTS_URI> --http-method=GET --oauth-service-account-email=<SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL>
```
